README
------------------------------------------------------
|   Mighty Chromium Installer and Updater  Readme    |
------------------------------------------------------
| This Mighty Python Script downloads and installs   |
| or updates lastest Chromium build snapshot for OSX |
------------------------------------------------------
|     For the lastest Stable Release of Python3      |
|     http://python.org/download/releases/3.3.0/     |
------------------------------------------------------
| In order to use this script, you need to give      |
| executable permissions with chmod. Also you can    |
| execute it manually. (eg. "$ Python chromium.py")  |
